2.	Total cost incurred and paid of the Real Estate Project as per books of accounts verified till 31/12/2023 is Rs. 22,73,81,200/-, however, the same is calculated higher by the RERA portal as Rs. 23,49,99,764/-. Consequent to this Proportion of the Cost incurred and paid on Land Cost and Construction Cost to the Total Estimated Cost is calculated as 100% by the RERA portal instead of actual at 96.76%.

3.	The amount which can be withdrawn from the Designated Account (Total Estimated Cost *Proportion of cost incurred and paid)  as per books of accounts verified till 31/12/2023 is Rs. 22,73,81,200/-, however, the same is calculated higher by the RERA portal as Rs. 23,49,99,764/. 4.	Estimated Balance Cost to Complete the Real Estate Project as per books of accounts verified till 31/12/2023 is Rs. 76,18,800/-, however the RERA portal calculates the same as Rs. 236/-.

All the above anomaly is caused as the RERA portal captures estimated cost instead of actual cost incurred and paid as per books of accounts which are verified till 31/12/2023.
